      "comment_id" : 42299920,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "To eliminate a stray XML declaration, you have to treat the file as text, not XML, because an extra XML declaration prevents the XML from being <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/a/25830482/290085\"><b>well-formed</b></a>.  Use a text editor or open the file programmatically and operate on it as <i>text</i> to eliminate the stray <b><code>&lt;?xml ?&gt;</code></b> declaration <i>before</i> treating it as an XML file."
