      "body" : "I am having a peculiar problem with this error. I download a file automatically, save it and process it to store the contents in a database. As you mentioned, my xml file has a xml declaration at the middle of the file. But, the error does not always appear. If it fails first time and I re-run the code, it passes. Sometimes, it fails 2-3 times and passes when I run it for the next time. In production environment, it has never failed, even though I am downloading the same file and using the same code."
