      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "You have my sympathies as intermittent problems are notoriously difficult to debug.  However, I cannot help more from here other than to tell you that this error is <b>definitely deterministic</b>: It will <b><i>always</i></b> be an error for an XML declaration to appear more than once or anywhere other than the top of an XML file.  Good luck."
