    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Debug your XML file. Either there is space or added extra or fewer tags.</p>\n<p>For better understanding build the project through the command line. Windows: <code>gradlew build</code></p>\n<p>In my case, AndroidManifest.xml has a blank space at the very first line</p>\n<pre><code>&lt;Empty Row&gt; // This Creates the issue \n&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
